metadata.name: Carpetdiem #0001
metadata.description:
This artwork is proof that there is magic in mathematics. Taking your eyes away from this mesmerising display of fractal geometry, which unfolds like a blossoming flower, is almost impossible. The artwork has a lure that beckons its viewers from afar and holds them captive, like magic. Indeed, this is a magic carpet.

If you are the owner of this NFT, you can access the high-resolution media files from the link below:

Collector Page: [https://www.carpetdiem.art/mycarpet/](https://www.carpetdiem.art/mycarpet/) 

NFT Details: [https://www.carpetdiem.art/mycarpet/1](https://www.carpetdiem.art/mycarpet/1) 

Generative Version: [https://www.carpetdiem.art/generative/1](https://www.carpetdiem.art/generative/1)
